# Place the following three files here before building:
#
#   AmazonRootCA1.pem  — AWS Root CA (same for every project)
#   claim.crt          — Claim (bootstrap) certificate from AWS IoT
#   claim.key          — Claim private key from AWS IoT
#
# These are SHARED across all devices — one set for the entire fleet.
# See README.md for setup instructions.
#
# DO NOT commit real certificate files to git.
